{"tid":2082970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"因為DQ，而反對參選既人犯左個錯誤","createTime":"2020-06-28T12:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:46:41.000Z","uid":69696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab389eeeb57ead8c14aca205c2a9d5f379efa107","tid":2082970,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預期性服從（Anticipatory obedience）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n〝大部分威權政體（Authoritarianism）的權力是人民無條件奉上的。在這種時刻，人民會預先設想比現在更高壓的政府會想要什麼，不等政府開口便主動服從。公民的這種行為，讓統治者明白政治權力的威能有多大。〞<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">暴政：掌控關鍵年代的獨裁風潮</div><br />\n<br />\n暴政既電子書：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/qn0l03\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2Fqn0l03&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=075c8b49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/qn0l03</a>"},{"pid":"76aafbd41742afc9c956ce2edeb69e12198c8b8e","tid":2082970,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1eadd3614d19fe281bc972bf247d5d23e7203e7","tid":2082970,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82be8738c65174339aa1a3841686f9f85e4a5c88","tid":2082970,"uid":26179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"白票撚不願面對"},{"pid":"e6a22556e99bbd67d1587ab8c8870a3a324c770d","tid":2082970,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"【置頂】<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選戰告急</strong></span></span> 倒數十星期 立即十星期拉票行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2082608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih